<img src="diamond.gif" hspace="5" align="top"><b>The Future of Medical Innovation: <a href="new-approach-med.html">A New Approach For Bringing Medical Products to Market</a></b> by Thomas Lenard, Ralph Epstein, Robert Tollison, W. Kip Viscusi and William M. Wardell <br>
<img src="diamond.gif" hspace="5" align="top"><b>The Future of Medical Innovation: <a href="tom4.html">Reaping the Benefits of the Knowledge Revolution</a></b> by Thomas Lenard and Brian Mannix<br>
<img src="diamond.gif" hspace="5" align="top"><a href="/pff/mip/pr020796.html"><b>Plan Kicks off FDA Reform</a></b>
</ul>
<a name="speeches"></a>

<img src="bullet.gif" hspace="5" align="top"><big>Speeches</big>
<ul>
