10. No one has suggested they need to add more chlorine to the drinking water.
<p>
9. The Democratic National Convention will not be held in Aspen.
<p>
8. The Republican National Convention will not be held in Aspen.
<p>
7. Former Governor Richard Lamm will be at the Reform <br>
Party Convention
, which also will not be held in Aspen.
<p>
6. You have a better chance to see gold in Aspen than in Atlanta.
<p> 
