http://www.lead-inst.org:80/pff/mip/intro.html 204.71.237.80 19970217140201 text/html 7627
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Monday, 17-Feb-97 14:02:51 GMT
Last-modified: Thursday, 11-Jul-96 19:36:13 GMT
