<DOCNO>WT10-B18-141</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA050-000867-B013-161</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.lead-inst.org:80/nmp/wr-1295.html 204.71.237.80 19970210130845 text/html 12333
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Monday, 10-Feb-97 13:09:31 GMT
Last-modified: Friday, 08-Dec-95 21:28:22 GMT
Content-length: 12149
