http://www.lead-inst.org:80/atr/supercon.html 204.71.237.80 19970210115941 text/html 3170
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Monday, 10-Feb-97 12:00:26 GMT
Last-modified: Tuesday, 07-May-96 17:47:53 GMT
