<html><head><title> Property Rights Initiatives--8/8/95 -- ATR</title></head><body bgcolor="#FFFFFF">
<center><h3>PROPERTY RIGHTS INITIATIVES  8/8/95</h3></center>
<HR><a href="/atr/1.html">ATR Home</a><P>
<a name="Index"<P></a>
<center><b>States with property rights initiative measures</b><br>
<a href="#Arizona">Arizona</a>
 | <a href="#California">California</a>
 | <a href="#Colorado">Colorado</a>
 | <a href="#Florida">Florida</a>
 | <a href="#Idaho">Idaho</a>
 | <a href="#Maine">Maine</a>
 | <a href="#Massachusetts">Massachusetts</a>
 | <a href="#Nebraska">Nebraska</a>
 | <a href="#North_Dakota">North Dakota</a>
 | <a href="#Oklahoma">Oklahoma</a>
 | <a href="#Oregon">Oregon</a>
 | <a href="#South_Dakota">South Dakota</a>
 | <a href="#Washington">Washington</a>
<P>
<hr size="6"></center>
<pre>
<font size="+3"><B>STATE	LEGISLATION</b></font> 
<hr size="6">
<a name="Arizona">ARIZONA		-Exempt all personal property from taxation       
<hr>
<a name="California"></a>CALIFORNIA	-Mobile home rent assistance and rent 
			control restrictions
<hr>
<a name="Colorado"></a>COLORADO	-Public right in water
		-Changes in property tax #3
<hr>
<a name="Florida"></a>FLORIDA		-Compensation for government damage of
			property values
<hr>
<a name="Idaho"></a>IDAHO		-Property tax reductions
<hr>
<a name="Massachusetts"></a>MASSACHUSETTS	-Protecting the rivers of the commonwealth
		-Wildlife and ecology protection act
		-Wildlife protection act
<hr>
<a name="Maine"></a>MAINE		-1% Property tax cap
<hr>
<a name="North_Dakota"></a>NORTH DAKOTA	-Environmental protection act
<hr>
<a name="Nebraska"></a>NEBRASKA	-Property tax relief
<hr>
<a name="Oklahoma"></a>OKLAHOMA	-Property tax reductions
<hr>
<a name="Oregon"></a>OREGON		-Property tax cap and cut
		-Standards for all mines and restoration 
			sites
		-Restrict clear-cutting and use of 
			pesticides
